Source: bootsplash
Section: base
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Razvan Gavril <razvan.g@plutohome.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4.0.0), libfreetype6-dev (>= 2.1.7-2.4), libjpeg62-dev (>= 6b-10), libmng-dev (>= 1.0.8-1), zlib1g-dev (>= 1)
Standards-Version: 3.6.1

Package: bootsplash
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, bootsplash-theme-linuxmce | bootsplash-theme-pluto | bootsplash-theme-monster | bootsplash-theme
Recommends: sysv-rc (>= 2.86.ds1-1pluto)
Replaces: bootsplash-theme-pluto, bootsplash-theme-monster
Description: Bootsplash user space utilities and scripts.
 Bootsplash utilites work with a bootsplash patched kernel to help displaying a nice
 splash screen on system startup. These package contains utitities and scripts that are
 used internaly by bootsplash to draw text and play animations.
